-------------Timestamp

---extracting the month,day,hour and year from the timestamp and checking the recent year and early year of the timestamp
select timestamp,
monthname(timestamp) as month,
dayname(timestamp) as day,
hour(timestamp) as hour,
year(timestamp) as year,
max (year(timestamp)) as recent_year,
min(year(timestamp)) as starting_year
from customers.conversion.data
group by timestamp;


